title: Triplast White Bubble Padded Envelopes - Pick Qty & Size: 50 x 1/A (100x165mm) A6 Envelopes - Large Letter Postal Bags with Bubble Wrap Lining and Peel & Seal Strip for Royal Mail Shipping & Postage
features: CONTENTS: Pack of 50 x White Bubble Envelopes | SIZE CODE: 1/A (A/000 equivalent) | INTERNAL USABLE AREA: 100x165mm | POSTAL CLASSIFICATION: Large Letter for Royal Mail | SUITABLE FOR: 1-10 Sheets of A6 Paper & Small Items | MADE in UK

BUILT TO PROTECT: Featuring a tear-resistant & robust 75gsm kraft paper exterior, shock-absorbing bubble wrap interior, and 10mm wide continuously sealed burst-proof seams, these parcel bags are designed to withstand rough handling & prevent damage

SAVE TIME & MONEY: Equipped with easy peel & seal strips, these lightweight cushioned postal bags boost packing speed & efficiency whilst also cutting down postage costs - a convenient and cost-effective alternative to bulky boxes, void fill & tape!

ECO-CONSCIOUS: Made from 50% recycled material, these bubble mailers are also 100% recyclable - follow the instructions printed on each bag to separate the FSC-graded kraft paper outer (PAP 22) from the bubble wrap lining (LDPE 4) before recycling

A PACKAGING ESSENTIAL: Widely used by ecommerce & retail stores, these postage bags are perfect for shipping documents, physical media, clothing, small electronics, etc. Customise with handwritten notes, stamps, or labels for a personal touch!
description: Product Description Triplast White Bubble Padded Envelopes offer a durable and eco-conscious mailing solution, ideal for protecting your items during transit. Widely used by ecommerce & retail stores to post all sorts of items - from flat items like books, catalogues, CDs & DVDs to odd-shaped items like small electronics, automotive parts & clothing - these bubble mailers come with easy peel & seal strips , allowing you to pack quickly and securely without the need for extra materials like boxes or tape. Their lightweight design helps reduce postage costs, making them a cost-effective option for businesses and individuals alike. These padded mailers feature a dual-layer design consisting of a robust 75gsm kraft paper exterior that resists tears , coupled with a shock-absorbing bubble wrap interior to safeguard against impacts . The 10mm wide continuously sealed seams ensure your parcels won’t burst, providing reliable protection for all your shipments. In addition to their protective qualities, these bubble envelopes are an eco-conscious choice. Made from 50% recycled materials , they are also 100% recyclable. Each envelope includes printed instructions to guide you in separating the FSC-graded kraft paper outer (PAP 22) from the bubble wrap lining (LDPE 4) for responsible recycling. Choose Triplast White Bubble Padded Envelopes for a cost-efficient postal packaging solution that combines robust protection with sustainability.
